title: 2443 S. Race Street - Across from DU!
posting_body: ['TEXT', 'show contact info', 'NOW FOR MORE INFO!', 'Virtual tour: 2443 S Race Street', 'AREA: Denver - University of Denver / DU', 'FEATURES: Walk to DU!', 'Beautiful, bright, clean duplex unit with wood floors and fresh paint.', 'Large backyard and patio (shared with 1 other unit)', 'INCLUDED UTILITIES:', 'Landscaping/lawn care, water, sewer, trash removal!', 'TENANT PAID UTILITIES:', 'All other utilities not listed above paid by tenant.', 'BEDROOMS & BATHROOMS: 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom.', 'KITCHEN APPLIANCES INCLUDED: Refrigerator (icemaker in freezer does not function ("as-is")-no water line is run, ice cube trays would need to be used), Stove, Microwave, Dishwasher, Garbage Disposal!', 'LAUNDRY:', 'Stackable washer/dryer in the unit!', 'FLOORING: Hardwood and tile.', 'HEAT/COOLING: Gas heat, swamp cooler AC.', 'PARKING: Detached garage (single stall available) and ample street parking!', 'Note: you must secure a parking pass from the city of Denver for street parking.', 'FENCING:', 'Fully Fenced Backyard (shared with other unit of duplex)!', 'BASEMENT: N/A', 'PETS: Up to 2 pets considered with a one-time, non-refundable pet fee of $250 per pet.', 'Sorry, but we cannot allow any of the following breeds of dog: American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, and Staffordshire Bull Terrier.', 'SECURITY DEPOSIT:', "Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", 'APPLICATION FEE: $30 per adult.', 'Please note we have a 700 minimum credit score for all properties.', 'AVAILABILITY DATE: July 25th!!', "**Applicants must be able to start a lease within 1 week of the property's listed availability date.", '**', 'LEASE TERM: Initial lease to end April through June of 2023 with 12-month extensions possible at that time.', 'Growing marijuana inside or outside the premises is not allowed, smoking of any kind inside the property is not allowed.', 'Minimum 700 credit score required.']
